title: Join GTA+ for Benefits
headline: Join GTA+ for Benefits
subtitle: 2X GTA$ on Priority FIB Files
content:
Join Grand Theft Auto Online's premium Membership program, delivering exclusive benefits and rewards to GTA+ Members each month, including GTA$500,000 and more.

Take on Terrorbyte Client Jobs from your cutting-edge command truck for 2X GTA$ and RP and join forces with former FIB agent Jodi Marshall to prepare and carry out Priority FIB Files to earn 2X GTA$ through February 5.

GTA+ automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
